{"tid":1772265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「甜心」員工被捕 機管局即割席","createTime":"2019-12-06T12:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T14:48:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1521f6ece84d01230adeb7fd06e14427e9396b9","tid":1772265,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191206/QUXLKTKY53MNZVRYI7IRRCFAWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191206%2FQUXLKTKY53MNZVRYI7IRRCFAWM%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrucrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=6a36c3ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191206%2FQUXLKTKY53MNZVRYI7IRRCFAWM%2F&h=08e47616\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191206/QUXLKTKY53MNZVRYI7IRRCFAWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n「甜心」員工被捕 機管局即割席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一場反送中運動喚起港人良知，令無數人選擇站得更前。90後糖水店老闆Leo由請學生試食糖水、深水埗遊行期間派糖水贈途人，甚至於10.1被捕後，失去機場管理局工作，但他坦言從未後悔，因面對極權政府，已沒有退縮這項選擇，「作為香港人就係要企出來！」<br />\n<br />\n位於長沙灣福榮街糖水店「甜一刻」於10.1突然有大批警員殺到，Leo被警方以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器及藏有工具可作非法用途罪名拘捕，之後獲准以5,000元保釋。他指被捕一刻沒有太驚慌，反而保釋後，收到公司解僱電郵更感愕然。他在機管局的飛行區運作部工作三年多，一直盡心盡力工作，卻在10月3日下午收到公司通知中止僱傭合約，並給予一個月通知金。他曾傳送電郵要求交代解僱原因，卻不獲回覆，「冇任何交代突然被（機管局）割咗席，真係一場白色恐怖，當你未定罪，冇做錯就咁樣炒咗」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191206/large/1575562660_4e64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191206%2Flarge%2F1575562660_4e64.jpg&h=3bc51d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLeo慨嘆不捨機管局的同事。梁志永攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生意好轉 增聘同路人<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：海外專家早倡獨立機構調查<br />\n<br />\n有失必有得，近月不少街坊都親自來到店舖為Leo打氣，他亦認識一些同聲同氣的食肆老闆，「有啲（客人）日日都落嚟，好似糖水可以當飯食咁」。數月來店舖生意轉好，他增聘五、六個來自不同背景的兼職員工，有學生記者，亦有人因與家人政見不同，另覓地方居住。他指，店舖需要人幫忙，正好互補所需，「佢哋喺呢度做嘢又開心，我請到佢哋又開心」，身為老闆，除了包員工伙食外，也會充當他們的樹洞，聆聽其煩惱，為他們解憂。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李思潁"},{"pid":"6e70ae7d14db8edaec487a77bf09459ac0d02476","tid":1772265,"uid":49643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e09d036e1d02afcfc3e5b8de5f28f668a434df","tid":1772265,"uid":251945,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"建議裝修機管局高層"},{"pid":"7aef7db55ef799f832df588880b9dc62ac9c52cc","tid":1772265,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bcad40235e88bf2d1b16b9b1f1f679f93c2247","tid":1772265,"uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"秘lo?"},{"pid":"8d0f8f226eca243503694e9e1f1c506eae5b5e3c","tid":1772265,"uid":279356,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"要寫機管局入小器簿<br />\n聽清算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff266410e9b74642f0c8d2982b41a56b7bcdd70","tid":1772265,"uid":326712,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8d0f8f226eca243503694e9e1f1c506eae5b5e3c","tid":1772265,"uid":279356,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"要寫機管局入小器簿<br />\n聽清算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"機管局好耐都係咁啦<br />\n梁振英個女果單野仲記唔記得"},{"pid":"0f76f8930ca5be1bebd715496639f888ee611046","tid":1772265,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持"},{"pid":"d5336107ab13270aaaf4e153b59029b8167345c9","tid":1772265,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c88a185cae328adbfc063e32f6980edd5e9821","tid":1772265,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"機管局高層班豬狗,同狗鐵一樣, 都係香港人養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}